    • Method Detail

      • getPartial

        public java.lang.Boolean getPartial()
        Boolean which indicates whether we need to operate on clone for the entire Application or for set of array replication groups. By default it is set to false, and consider that clones to be operated for all array replication groups in an Application. If set to true, volumes list should be provided with full copy URIs one from each Array replication group. In any case, minimum of one full copy URI needs to be specified in order to identify the clone set.
